12) The one extra thing that @Repository has (which @Component or @Service does NOT) is:

repository has extra feature know as Exception Translation means when something fails in db like key is missing, data missing, sql expection 
these low level expection are combined under one common exception so it is easy to handle, so instead of having multiple catch blocks for each 
db-level exception we can have common expection



